data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. You'll want to take a look at this incredible opportunity to OWN a very strong 2/2/1 that easily could be converted to a 3 bedroom with very little effort!! This half acre double lot is very neatly tucked in the middle of all things Port Charlotte and Northport for ABSOLUTE convenience!! Not many homes go on sale in this neighborhood because it boasts so many conveniences for work, schools, shopping, water  sports, leisure, pet parks and much, much more ...ALL just minutes from your own massive back yard if you decide that you just want to stay at home with family & friends. Awesome real wood kitchen cabinets that line the granite counter tops amidst a fully stainless steel ensemble of appliances. Kitchen has the luxury of a pass through to the Florida room, a large pantry and equipped with a reverse osmosis system. Florida room was an addition to the home and makes the numbers somewhat deceiving because it actually connects to a lanai which makes for a Great family space. Your master has a walk-in closet easily fit for two!! Living room has a rare coat and shoe closet also great for storage. Property may have a first with not one but two very large car ports and a large storage shed to house any tools or toys!! Both carports have been graced with decorative pavers that make this one a keeper forever. Large family outings are no Big Deal. Both baths have been recently updated with tile and granite. The entire property, has been aligned with a recently installed vinyl fence!! Your pets can enjoy lots of outdoor space with freedom to roam and play. Water heater, A/C and windows have all been upgraded as well. No roof worries here...this one is metal!! Landscaping is very mature and well kept, graces the entrance to the property. Your home will be  equipped with an above ground pool and decorative lighting throughout the entire yard. Less than a 30 minute drive if you choose to go fishing or swimming if you should feel the need to step away from ALL OF THIS pleasure? You would need to create a way not to enjoy every wakening moment of this beautifully built, well placed home in one of our nicest neighborhoods around. NONE of the things that families love to do shall be compromised with this arrangement of pure quality!! Come see this gem however you may, but you won't be disappointed from front to back!!  MUST SEE ASAP!!!
